{"tid":2076182,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲Super Girls成員陳穎欣出演Viu地產新劇","createTime":"2020-06-23T10:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T08:58:49.000Z","uid":44730,"like":45,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"4b804a9071710d910a95a0b3b806e83d6a9b9666","tid":2076182,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"Super Girls成員陳穎欣（Yanny）近年轉戰影視圈，繼去年在ViuTV劇集《仇老爺爺》擔正女主角後，今年又有份參演即將上映的ViuTV新劇《地產仔》，飾演鄭浩南手下一名地產經紀「欣豬」，為演好角色，Yanny更專程到地產舖向真正的經紀取經<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/4_938749285ef1a20e7bdaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F4_938749285ef1a20e7bdaf.jpg&h=665a9959&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8d9de34f833727d0bdb698acedafaea75242662","tid":2076182,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"現年30歲的Yanny在2011年參加 《Icon Girls招募大賽》勝出，與趙慧珊 （Aka） 、蔡明芳（Jessica） 、吳嘉熙（Cheronna）及李靜儀 （Heidi）組成五人女子組合IconGirls，翌年組合改名為SuperGirls正式出道。<br />\n<br />\n今次陳穎欣與鄭浩南及吳肇軒等合作拍攝新劇《地產仔》，劇情一開始就會講到吳肇軒飾演的裝修工人「令狐飛」因仰Yanny飾演的地產經紀「欣豬」，而在陰差陽錯下加入了 「馬王」 （鄭浩南飾） 所創辦的 「和聯興地產」 工作，所以Yanny由頭到尾都會係女神Look"},{"pid":"dc532d4626b9ec68f522459f4b6e89730d5bb7cc","tid":2076182,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"在劇中Yanny是飾演一個比較怕事的職員，有不少被同事欺負的劇情，但Yanny表示拍攝過程非常開心，因為整個團隊的人都很有趣，平時又喜歡爆肚演出，因此常有笑料出現。而被問到和鄭浩南合作有什麼難忘事，Yanny就表示浩南哥每次出現都有一股懾人的氣勢，其中有一幕是要和浩南哥對抗，她笑言唯有用演技去戰勝這個氣勢。"},{"pid":"201028f05ace2aa2f2dfe71eaae6fe6fb58ffabc","tid":2076182,"uid":44730,"like":26,"dislike":7,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/12_13876354615ef1a124a1ad9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F12_13876354615ef1a124a1ad9.jpg&h=6dab4fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/13_18227222595ef1a1140877b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F13_18227222595ef1a1140877b.jpg&h=430938a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/yannyyc_104343647_1198065913880789_4300106948356180334_n_17043486915ef1a12328703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fyannyyc_104343647_1198065913880789_4300106948356180334_n_17043486915ef1a12328703.jpg&h=f0ed4118&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc6d223b6bef086077e33c3df8f01257977eb111","tid":2076182,"uid":184233,"like":9,"dislike":21,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"港女不了"},{"pid":"0f33c0ed6e994359d7eff1f276de48930a949d5f","tid":2076182,"uid":44730,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/71878356_2485061774892807_769692185648955392_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=9e2e56&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=L_75SlDntSoAX9xhHBr&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=14&amp;oh=5c876b583068e887c313f115348ca4b4&amp;oe=5F1807D9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F71878356_2485061774892807_769692185648955392_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D9e2e56%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_ohc%3DL_75SlDntSoAX9xhHBr%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D14%26oh%3D5c876b583068e887c313f115348ca4b4%26oe%3D5F1807D9&h=a56b5722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/56622585_2155473994539118_3607885447625179136_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=9e2e56&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=1GldmJw-imYAX-0k_Iz&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.xx